==English==
===Etymology===
First word of the {{L.}} phrase ''[[requiescat in pace]]'', "may he/she rest in peace"

===Pronunciation===
*(''[[RP]]''): /rɛkwɪˈɛskæt/, /<tt>rEkwI"Esk{t</tt>/
*(''US'') rĕk'wē-ĕsʹkăt, /ˌrɛkwiˈɛskæt/, /<tt>%rEkwi"Esk{t</tt>/

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[prayer]] for the [[peaceful]] [[repose]] of the [[soul]] of a [[dead]] person